					<outline text="Of course Scoble tops the list. I'll let you figure out what that means. I chuckled when I saw Guy Kawasaki coming in at #4. I guess his semi-spam pays off (if this means anything, which it doesn't -- see the disclaimer). " created="Sun, 27 Apr 2008 17:28:18 GMT"/>
